OL,6,F"You won't have to wait much longer to
OL,7,Fsee what the measures are. Some of
OL,8,Fthem are already in place, the free
OL,9,Fschool meals, the breakfast clubs, the
OL,10,Ffree childcare, are all part of it...
OL,11,FBut look, we need to do more than
OL,12,Fthat."
OL,14,FPressed by Doctor Amir Khan on whether
OL,15,Fthat will involve getting rid of the
OL,16,Ftwo-child limit on benefits, Starmer
OL,17,Fsaid: "I wouldn't be telling you we're
OL,18,Fgoing to drive down child poverty if I
OL,19,Fwasn't clear that we will be taking a
OL,20,Fnumber of measures in order to do so".
