OL,3,CStarmer hints controversial two-child
OL,4,Cbenefit cap will be axed in Budget
OL,6,FThe prime minister's comments come
OL,7,Fafter months of speculation and
OL,8,Freports that Reeves would partially
OL,9,Flift the cap by bringing in a tapered
OL,10,Fapproach, or limiting extra benefits
OL,11,Fto three or four children.
OL,13,FBut on Monday, the chancellor appeared
OL,14,Fto end that speculation when she gave
OL,15,Fthe strongest suggestion yet that the
OL,16,Fcap would be abolished in full.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
