OL,6,FThe chancellor said she does not think
OL,7,Fchildren should be "penalised" for
OL,8,Fbeing part of large families, adding
OL,9,Fthat "we'll take further measures" to
OL,10,Fend child poverty in the Budget later
OL,11,Fthis month.
OL,13,FITV News understands ministers have
OL,14,Fbeen told the government is planning
OL,15,Fto lift the cap, following increasing
OL,16,Fpressure from within the Labour Party,
OL,17,Fincluding from former prime minister
OL,18,Fand chancellor Gordon Brown.
