OL,6,F"There are plenty of reasons why
OL,7,Fpeople make decisions to have three,
OL,8,Ffour children, but then find
OL,9,Fthemselves in difficult times.
OL,11,F"Lots and lots of different reasons
OL,12,Fwhy families change shape and size
OL,13,Fover time, and I don't think that it's
OL,14,Fright that a child is penalised
OL,15,Fbecause they are in a bigger family
